---
const phoneNumber = "(419) 345-7778";
const phoneHref = "tel:+141****7778";
---

<section class="about section" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-layout">
      <div class="about-content">
        <div class="section-header reveal" style="text-align:left">
          <span class="tag">About Great Lakes</span>
          <h2><span class="gradient-text">Independent. Local. Accountable.</span></h2>
          <div class="divider" style="margin:1rem 0 1.5rem"></div>
        </div>

        <p class="about-body reveal">
          Great Lakes Insurance Solutions was founded by Ohio natives who saw a problem: big insurance companies treating customers like policy numbers. We built something different — an independent agency that works for you, not the carrier.
        </p>

        <p class="about-body reveal">
          We represent over 20 top-rated insurance carriers, which means we can shop around for the best coverage at the best price — without pushing a single product just because it pays better.
        </p>

        <div class="about-stats stagger">
          <div class="stat-item reveal">
            <span class="stat-num">20+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Carrier Partners</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item reveal">
            <span class="stat-num">12K+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Ohio Families Protected</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item reveal">
            <span class="stat-num">98%</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Claims Satisfaction</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item reveal">
            <span class="stat-num">16</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Years in Business</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-ctas reveal">
          <a href={phoneHref} class="btn btn-primary">Talk to an Agent</a>
          <a href="#products" class="btn btn-outline">View Our Products</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-visual reveal">
        <div class="about-card">
          <div class="about-card-header">
            <span class="card-badge">Why Independent?</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="about-benefits">
            <li>
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              <span>We work for YOU, not the insurance company</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              <span>Access to 20+ carriers — not just one</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              <span>Average savings of $847/yr with bundling</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              <span>Local agents who answer the phone</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              <span>Claims handled by real people in Ohio</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: var(--stone-warm);
  }

  .about-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-body {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .stat-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--navy);
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .about-ctas {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .about-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 2px solid var(--gold);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(196, 154, 44, 0.12);
  }

  .about-card-header {
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
  }

  .card-badge {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .about-benefits {
    list-style: none;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about-benefits li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .about-benefits svg { flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
</style>